title: 이달의소녀탐구 #370 (LOONA TV #370)
summary:
0:01 -- The rehearsals for the second day end.
0:10 -- The girls have a surprise waiting. They received lunch from their fans.
0:17 -- Hye: "Thank You!"; YeoJin: "Such an amazing gift." They all thank one by one.
0:29 -- HyunJin (while keeping her face close to her box): "HyunJin's Food" and proceeds to bite the air around the box. (What a meme)
0:33 -- Lippie mentions that HeeJin mentioned to her that she wanted to have asparagus and that she said to her that she wanted to eat meat. Now they get to eat both.
0:45 -- Yves: "I am eating lunch that was provided by our fans. I can't remember when was the alst time I had such amazing food." (smh BBC feed them good food)
0:51 -- YeoJin: "YVES IS THE BEST!!!!"
0:54 -- All the students watching from the side of the sister know! [I believe my translation is wonky here!]
